Title: The Abu Alaa Mansour Collection

AltTitle.other: List of names of prisoners sentenced for life in the prisons of the Israeli occupation

References: Mansour, Abu Alaa, "Correspondence and Reports," private collection, August 2018, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.

Title: توضيح حول إحصائية أسرى الانتفاضة الاولى من 1987 - 1990
AltTitle.other: Clarification regarding the statistics on the prisoners of the First Intifada in 1987 - 1990
Description.note: The number of prisoners arrested during the three years of the Intifada between 1987 and 1990 is estimated at around 120 thousand cases of arrest, the estimates included all cases of arrest beginning with 48 hour arrests and up to 3 life sentences. These statistics were taken from a random sample of prisoners amounting to 25 thousand of those who spent 3 or more months in prison at the time.|~|يقدر عدد الاسرى الذين تم اعتقالهم خلال سنوات الانتفاضة الثلاث من 1987 - 1990 بحوالي 120 ألف حالة اعتقال، وقد تضمن العدد كافة حالات الاعتقال من 48 ساعة حتى الثلاثة مؤبدات. هذه الإحصائية أجريت على شريحة عشوائية من الأسرى عددها 25 ألف أسير ممن أمضو في المعتقلات ثلاثة شهور فأكثر وبقوا رهن الاعتقال أنذاك.
References: Mansour, Abu Alaa, "Correspondence and Reports," private collection, August 2018, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.
Description (Eng): The number of prisoners arrested during the three years of the Intifada between 1987 and 1990 is estimated at around 120 thousand cases of arrest, the estimates included all cases of arrest beginning with 48 hour arrests and up to 3 life sentences. These statistics were taken from a random sample of prisoners amounting to 25 thousand of those who spent 3 or more months in prison at the time.

Title: إحصائية تبين كيفية استشهاد عدد من شهداء الثورة الفلسطينية
AltTitle.other: Statistics showing how a number of shaheeds of the Palestinian Revolt came to be
Description.note: The statistics show the list of shaheeds registered at the Association for Social Affairs and Caring for the Families of Shaheeds and Prisoners in Amman only, and not necessarily the total number of shaheeds of the revolution in the various sites.|~|تناولت الإحصائية الشهداء المعتمدين في مؤسسة الشؤون الاجتماعية لرعاية أسر الشهداء والأسرى في عمان فقط، وليس بالضرورة أن تتطابق مع العدد الكلي لشهداء الثورة في المواقع المختلفة.
References: Mansour, Abu Alaa, "Correspondence and Reports," private collection, August 2018, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.
